277
00:33:36,456 --> 00:33:39,540
Da imaš i grIiš

278
00:33:39,751 --> 00:33:44,045
I ponekad se ne sIožiš

279
00:33:46,716 --> 00:33:49,753
O, divno je

280
00:33:50,721 --> 00:33:55,679
Živeti za nekoga

281
00:33:59,813 --> 00:34:04,143
Najvrednija stvar koju imaš da daš je

282
00:34:04,944 --> 00:34:07,731
Tvoja Ijubav

283
00:34:09,907 --> 00:34:14,320
